- [[Set GCP Project]] to your target project
- [[Get Cluster Name of a Specific Gke]] you can get **location**, cluster name etc with this command

``` shell
gcloud container clusters upgrade CLUSTER_NAME \
  --node-pool=NODE_NAME \
  --project=PROJECT_NAME \
  --location=europe-west1-b \
  --cluster-version 1.33.4-gke.1245000
```
